RapidSVN is a cross-platform GUI front-end for the Subversion revision system 
written in C++ using the wxWindows framework. This project also includes a 
Subversion client C++ API.

Features

* Simple - provides an easy to use interface for Subversion features
* Efficient - simple for beginners but flexible enough to increase 
  productivity for experienced Subversion users
* Portable - runs on any platform in Subversion and wxWindows can run: Linux, 
  Windows, Mac OS 9/X, Solaris, etc.
* Fast - entirely written in C++ 
